Reasoning: The paper presents a complete simultaneous localization and mapping (SLAM) system for monocular, stereo and RGB-D cameras, which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV). The system also includes loop closing and relocalization capabilities, which involve machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The evaluation of the system on public sequences also involves computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR).
